stant settlement, transparent transactions, and programmable financial services.",marks:[],data:{}}]},{nodeType:"paragraph",data:{},content:[{nodeType:"text",value:"Consensys contributes to every major protocol upgrade, building and maintaining the execution and consensus clients that secure the network.",marks:[],data:{}}]}]},bottomSpacer:false,id:"homepage-from-the-merge-to-pectra-and-beyond"}},{metadata:{tags:[],concepts:[]},sys:{space:{sys:{type:"Link",linkType:"Space",id:"gjyjx7gst9lo"}},id:"24vMsHgojd9cESz0RVNISr",type:"Entry",createdAt:"2025-12-04T09:51:03.642Z",updatedAt:"2025-12-04T09:51:03.642Z",environment:{sys:{id:"master",type:"Link",linkType:"Environment"}},publishedVersion:1,revision:1,contentType:{sys:{type:"Link",linkType:"ContentType",id:"moduleSectionNew"}},locale:"en-US"},fields:{name:"Homepage - Research Cards",component:"ResearchCards",theme:"dark",list:[{metadata:{tags:[],concepts:[]},sys:{space:{sys:{type:"Link",linkType:"Space",id:"gjyjx7gst9lo"}},id:"7yQhM9HTANuRpBTC2zlLQ6",type:"Entry",createdAt:"2025-12-04T09:50:55.036Z",updatedAt:"2025-12-04T09:50:55.036Z",environment:{sys:{id:"master",type:"Link",linkType:"Environment"}},publishedVersion:1,revision:1,contentType:{sys:{type:"Link",linkType:"ContentType",id:"listItemSimple"}},locale:"en-US"},fields:{internalName:"Pectra Home research card",title:"The Pectra upgrade to the execution and consensus layers introduced Smart Accounts and other powerful features",eyebrow:"PECTRA",image:{metadata:{tags:[],concepts:[]},sys:{space:{sys:{type:"Link",linkType:"Space",id:"gjyjx7gst9lo"}},id:"2t3d2pAo5jjreI5nQCe5wb",type:"Asset",createdAt:"2025-12-04T09:46:58.922Z",updatedAt:"2025-12-04T09:46:58.922Z",environment:{sys:{id:"master",type:"Link",linkType:"Environment"}},publishedVersion:2,revision:1,locale:"en-US"},fields:{title:"pectra research",description:"",file:{url:"//images.ctfassets.net/gjyjx7gst9lo/2t3d2pAo5jjreI5nQCe5wb/b84bd113f3d684e1562e10fde034caed/pectra.png",details:{size:479410,image:{wid